1. *Nazvali* su me juče uveče. (They called me last night.)
2. Juče uveče su *nazvali* mene. (Last night they called me.)
3. Oni su me *nazvali* da potvrde dogovor. (They called me to confirm the agreement.)
4. *Nazvali* su me nakon što sam poslao mejl. (They called me after I sent the email.)
5. Oni su *nazvali* ovu kafanu po mom dedi. (They named this bar after my grandfather.)
6. Kada su me *nazvali*, bio sam na sastanku. (When they called me, I was in a meeting.)
7. Molim vas da *nazovete* restoran i rezervišete sto. (Please call the restaurant and reserve a table.)
8. Ja ću *nazvati* taksija da nas odveze do aerodroma. (I will call a taxi to take us to the airport.)
9. Da li možete da *nazovete* mene kada stignete? (Can you call me when you arrive?)
10. *Nazovimo* ovaj projekat "Novi početak". (Let's name this project "New Beginning".)